{"tid":2512940,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★犬決！北韓約一萬學生自首承認曾偷看韓劇 最高可被判處死刑","createTime":"2021-05-02T06:24:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T06:24:10.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"28902d9ad8c19612f087c068322f1d055e77c29f","tid":2512940,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T06:24:02.000Z","msg":"報道指單是一個城市已有一萬名學生自首，承認看過韓劇和電影，他們還向當局交出五千多部DVD播放器。<br />\n<br />\n根據《反動思想文化排斥法》，凡是引入或散播南韓電影、影片、書籍等的人，<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>最高可被判處死刑</strong></span>，安排他人集體觀看的人亦可判處死刑，至於偷看韓劇等的人士最高可被判監十五年，據報平壤當局已設立聯合小組專門搜查偷看韓劇的民眾。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=433233\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D433233&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNgxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=6004fe8c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D433233&h=30bc9907\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=433233</a>"},{"pid":"8f6f99925ec9c9a1628452dec3a8ae5161e5192f","tid":2512940,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T06:24:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}